the wicket of Thilan Samaraweera with the final ball of the day.
Tillakaratne Dilshan will be on 50 when play resumes tomorrow.  The teams are also scheduled to play matches in Melbourne
and Sydney. Sri Lanka failed to win any of its previous 10 Tests
